View a Comprehensive Summary of Patient’s Member Plans

This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise and Unlimited editions with Life Sciences Cloud or Health Cloud license.
Pharmacy Benefits Verification is available starting in June 2024.

Users with the Health Cloud Starter (for Life Sciences Cloud) or Health Cloud Foundation (for Health Cloud), and Manage Pharmacy Benefits Verification permission set can use this feature.

Add the PharmacyBenefitsVerification flexcard to the Care Program Enrollee record page.
